name: Mackenzie US Government Long Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive US 20+ Year Treasury Bond CAD Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in US long dated government debt instruments denominated in US dollars. The Portfolio seeks to provide capital appreciation.
